#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.198:0.2"
msgid "20. Brāhmaṇavagga "
msgstr "20. Brahmins "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: subhāsitavācāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.198:0.3"
msgid "198. Vācāsutta "
msgstr "198. Well-Spoken Words "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.244, sc1
#. VAR: ananuvajjā ca viññūnaṃ → ananuvajjā viññūnaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.198:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgatā vācā subhāsitā hoti, no dubbhāsitā, anavajjā ca ananuvajjā ca viññūnaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, speech that has five factors is well spoken, not poorly spoken. It’s blameless and is not criticized by sensible people. "

msgctxt "an5.198:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.198:1.3"
msgid "Kālena ca bhāsitā hoti, saccā ca bhāsitā hoti, saṇhā ca bhāsitā hoti, atthasaṃhitā ca bhāsitā hoti, mettacittena ca bhāsitā hoti. "
msgstr "It is speech that is timely, true, gentle, beneficial, and loving. "

msgctxt "an5.198:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi aṅgehi samannāgatā vācā subhāsitā hoti, no dubbhāsitā, anavajjā ca ananuvajjā ca viññūnan”ti. "
msgstr "Speech with these five factors is well spoken, not poorly spoken. It’s blameless and is not criticized by sensible people.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.198:1.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

